cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper deals with contextual word representations and their alignment in multilingual models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also discusses improvements in performance, which suggests that it could belong to the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Finally, the paper mentions analyzing and correcting deficiencies in the model, which could also place it in the computer vision and pattern recognition category (cs.CV).
